# Movie Recommendation System

This project recommends movies to users based on their preferences using Machine Learning techniques.
It helps users discover new movies similar to their interests.

## Features
- Content-based movie recommendations
- Similarity calculation using ML
- User-friendly recommendations
- Fast and efficient predictions

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- NLP (TF-IDF / Cosine Similarity)

## Dataset
- Source: MovieLens Dataset
- Data includes movie titles, genres, and ratings

## Workflow
1. Load and clean dataset
2. Feature extraction
3. Calculate similarity between movies
4. Generate movie recommendations
5. Display recommended movies

## How to Run
1. Clone the repository  
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/movie-recommendation-system.git

2. Install dependencies  
   pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Run the script  
   python recommendation.py

## Results
- Accurate recommendations based on movie similarity
- Efficient content-based filtering

## Future Enhancements
- Add collaborative filtering
- Improve recommendations using deep learning
- Deploy as a web application

